136},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":139,\"end\":142},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":143,\"end\":145},{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":170,\"end\":174}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":25}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"26\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":2167,\"number\":27,\"text\":\"وَاتْلُ مَآ اُوْحِيَ اِلَيْكَ مِنْ كِتَابِ رَبِّكَۗ  لَا مُبَدِّلَ لِكَلِمٰتِهٖۗ وَلَنْ تَجِدَ مِنْ دُوْنِهٖ مُلْتَحَدًا\",\"translation_id\":\"Bacakanlah (Nabi Muhammad) apa yang diwahyukan kepadamu, yaitu Kitab Tuhanmu (Al-Qur’an). Tidak ada yang dapat mengubah kalimat-kalimat-Nya dan engkau tidak akan dapat menemukan tempat berlindung selain kepada-Nya.\",\"juz_id\":15,\"surah_id\":18,\"transliteration\":\"watlu mâ ûḫiya ilaika ming kitâbi rabbik, lâ mubaddila likalimâtih, wa lan tajida min dûnihî multaḫadâ\",\"translation_en\":\"And recite, [O Muḥammad], what has been revealed to you of the Book of your Lord. There is no changer of His words, and never will you find in other than Him a refuge.\",\"translation_de\":\"Und verlies, was dir vom Buch deines Herrn (als Offenbarung) eingegeben worden ist. Es gibt niemanden, der Seine Worte abändern könnte, und du wirst außer (bei) Ihm keine Zuflucht finden.\",\"translation_tr\":\"Rabbinin Kitabı'ndan sana vahyedileni oku. Onun kelimelerini değiştirebilecek yoktur. O'ndan başka bir sığınak da bulamazsın.\",\"translation_fr\":\"Récite ce qui t’a été révélé du Livre de ton Seigneur. Nul ne peut modifier Ses paroles et, en dehors de Lui, tu ne trouveras aucun refuge.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":10,\"end\":13},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":33,\"end\":38},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":86,\"end\":91},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":98,\"end\":103}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":26}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"27\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":2168,\"number\":28,\"text\":\"وَاصْبِرْ نَفْسَكَ مَعَ الَّذِيْنَ يَدْعُوْنَ رَبَّهُمْ بِالْغَدٰوةِ وَالْعَشِيِّ يُرِيْدُوْنَ وَجْهَهٗ وَلَا تَعْدُ عَيْنٰكَ عَنْهُمْۚ تُرِيْدُ زِيْنَةَ الْحَيٰوةِ الدُّنْيَاۚ